OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fclear away northeastwards this
OL,7,Fevening. Then the rest if the night
OL,8,Fwill be largely dry although with a
OL,9,Flot of cloud. Fresh southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA mainly dry day although
OL,13,Fwith a good deal of cloud. The odd
OL,14,Fspot of rain possible in the far west.
OL,15,FSome brighter spells along the north
OL,16,Fcoast. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
