OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Wednesday then brighter with a
OL,7,Ffew showers. Breezy with a few showers
OL,8,Fon Thursday. Further rain likely on
OL,9,FFriday morning, followed by showers.
OL,10,FMild.
